C%20Discord.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECitron%20is%20stepping%20down%20as%20CEO%20and%20handing%20over%20the%20reins%20to%20a%20former%20Activision%20Blizzard%20executive.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECitron%20said%20he%20has%20a%20backlog%20of%20three%20games%20that%20he%20wants%20to%20complete%20after%20stepping%20down.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-discord%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDiscord%3C%2Fa%3E%20cofounder%20Jason%20Citron%2C%2040%2C%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20he%20will%20be%20stepping%20down%20as%20CEO%20of%20the%20messaging%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20be%20transitioning%20to%20a%20new%20role%20as%20board%20member%20and%20advisor%2C%20and%20continuing%20to%20support%20Discord%20through%20this%20next%20chapter%2C%26quot%3B%20Citron%20wrote%20in%20an%20X%20post%20on%20Wednesday.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20incredibly%20proud%20of%20what%20we've%20built%20together%20%E2%80%94%20and%20even%20more%20excited%20for%20what's%20ahead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECitron%20told%20the%20tech%20news%20publication%20VentureBeat%20that%20he%20doesn't%20have%20any%20concrete%20post-retirement%20plans%20lined%20up%2C%20though%20he%20will%20be%20spending%20more%20time%20with%20his%20family%20and%20on%20gaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20specific%20plans%20for%20myself.%20I'll%20maybe%20take%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20break%20to%20spend%20time%20with%20my%20kids%2C%26quot%3B%20Citron%20said%2C%20adding%20there%20were%20three%20games%20on%20his%20to-play%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20need%20to%20finish%20Final%20Fantasy%20VII%20Rebirth.%20I%20have%20a%20backlog.%20I%20want%20to%20play%20Blue%20Prince.%20I%20haven't%20even%20played%20Baldur's%20Gate%20III%2C%20believe%20it%20or%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Citron%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRebirth%26quot%3B%20is%20the%202024%20sequel%20to%20the%20blockbuster%20%26quot%3BFinal%20Fantasy%20VII%26quot%3B%20remake%2C%20a%20landmark%20release%20by%20the%20Japanese%20studio%20Square%20Enix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20%26quot%3BBaldur's%20Gate%20III%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20fantasy%20adventuring%20game%20based%20loosely%20on%20%26quot%3BDungeons%20%26amp%3B%20Dragons%26quot%3B%20mechanics%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaldurs-gate-popularity-sales-character-creation-video-game-larian-studios-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereleased%20in%20August%202023%20to%20wide%20acclaim%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBlue%20Prince%2C%26quot%3B%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20a%20mystery%20and%20puzzle%20adventure%20game%20in%20which%20the%20player%20traverses%20a%20family%20estate%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20find%20the%20ever-elusive%2046th%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiscord%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20same%20day%20that%20the%20former%20vice%20chairman%20of%20Activision%20Blizzard%2C%20Humam%20Sakhnini%2C%20will%20be%20taking%20over%20from%20Citron%20as%20CEO%20from%20April%2028.%20Citron%20cofounded%20Discord%20in%202015%20with%20Stanislav%20Vishnevskiy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20job%20of%20a%20CEO%20is%20constantly%20evolving%2C%20and%20over%20the%20years%20I%20have%20continuously%20'hired%20myself%20out%20of%20a%20job.'%20Usually%2C%20that%20means%20delegating%20work%20and%20then%20taking%20on%20different%20leadership%20challenges%2C%26quot%3B%20Citron%20said%20in%20a%20blog%20post%20to%20Discord%20employees%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20as%20I%20look%20at%20what%20is%20needed%20of%20Discord's%20CEO%20over%20the%20next%20few%20years%2C%20I%20realize%20that%20it's%20time%20for%20me%20to%20literally%20'hire%20myself%20out%20of%20a%20job%2C'%26quot%3B%20Citron%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECitron%20said%20in%20his%20interview%20with%20VentureBeat%20that%20his%20decision%20to%20step%20back%20was%20based%20on%20who%20could%20%26quot%3Btake%20Discord%20to%20the%20next%20level.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20yo