ach%20something%20entirely%20new%2C%20say%2C%20computer%20science%2C%20without%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20that%20field%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKira%20has%20done%20this%20dance%20before.%20It%20launched%20in%202021%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20helping%20teachers%20without%20a%20background%20in%20computer%20science%20teach%20the%20subject%20effectively.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20several%20states%20were%20ramping%20up%20legislation%20around%20making%20computer%20science%20a%20requirement%20to%20graduate%20from%20high%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221090%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kira%20Learning%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68095c57c6ad288d147efb3f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22817%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKira%20Learning's%20team%2C%20chairman%20Andrew%20Ng%2C%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20Andrea%20Pasinetti%2C%20and%20cofounder%20and%20vice%20president%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20Jagriti%20Agarwal.%3Cp%3EKira%20Learning%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BComputer%20science%20started%20being%20introduced%20into%20high%20schools%20in%20a%20way%20that%20existed%20at%20parity%20with%20subjects%20like%20English%20and%20biology%20and%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20Andrea%20Pasinetti%2C%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Kira%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BBetween%20legislation%20being%20passed%20and%20it%20becoming%20a%20requirement%20for%20students%2C%20there%20was%20often%20a%20window%20of%20one%2C%20at%20most%20two%20years%2C%20and%20that%20required%20training.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20teachers%20quickly%20get%20up%20to%20speed%2C%20Kira%20developed%20AI%20tutors%20to%20help%20teachers%20master%20the%20subjects.%20It%20also%20developed%20AI%20teaching%20assistants%20to%20help%20them%20in%20the%20classroom.%20In%202023%2C%20it%20partnered%20with%20the%20state%20of%20Tennessee%20%E2%80%94%20an%20early%20adopter%20of%20this%20legislation%20%E2%80%94%20to%20roll%20out%20the%20platform%20to%20all%20public%20middle%20schools%20and%20high%20schools%20in%20the%20state.%20Its%20since%20been%20adopted%20in%20hundreds%20of%20school%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edistricts%20in%20states%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20company%20is%20expanding%20its%20platform%20to%20include%20all%20subjects.%20Its%20new%20suite%20of%20AI%20agents%20will%20help%20fulfill%20the%20company's%20ultimate%20goal%20of%20personalizing%20the%20learning%20process%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20Pasinetti%20said%20is%20%26quot%3Balmost%20impossible%26quot%3B%20today%2C%20given%20how%20understaffed%20schools%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22245993aa-7a74-4596-b9a2-0635617426f7%5C%22%3ESubverting%20AI%20to%20make%20learning%20better%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENg%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20AI%20and%20education.%20He's%20launched%20ed-tech%20companies%20like%20Coursera%2C%20and%20DeepLearning.AI%20%E2%80%94%20where%20his%20latest%20course%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandrew-ng-ai-learn-vibe-coding-course-replit-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVibe%20Coding%20101%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20is%20available.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20Forbes%20in%202014%2C%20he%20said%20that%20AI%20has%20the%20%26quot%3Bpotential%20to%20free%20up%20humanity%20from%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20mental%20drudgery.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20a%20decade%20later%20that%20notion%20has%20taken%20hold%20of%20the%20corporate%20world%20where%20workers%20are%20using%20AI%20to%20eliminate%20rote%20tasks%20like%20writing%20emails%2C%20analyzing%20data%2C%20and%20synthesizing%20research.%20However%2C%20what%20constitutes%20%26quot%3Bmental%20drudgery%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20education%20is%20less%20clear%2C%20especially%20as%20educators%20%E2%80%94%20and%20students%20%E2%80%94%20worry%20that%20the%20technology%20will%20make%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-college-students-use-ai-homework-study-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eskills%20stagnate%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKira%2C%20in%20some%20sense%2C%20is%20subverting%20the%20building%20blocks%20of%20generative%20AI%20to%20cut%20out%20the%20busywork%20and%20enhance%20the%20learning%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20underlying%20AI%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bfundamentally%20discursive%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20Pasinetti%20said.%20While%20the%20methodical%20nature%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecan%20help%20students%20work%20through%20material%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-chatgpt-ai-education-students-homework-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESocratic%20method%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20enabling%20a%20back-and-forth%20dialogue%20%E2%80%94%20the%20issue%20is%20that%20it's%20also%20designed%20to%20deliver%20answers%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible%2C%20Pasinetti%20said.%20Several%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20generative%20AI%20chatbots%20are%20also%20in%20a%20race%20against%20Google%20to%20become%20the%20world's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-search-default-web-browser-engine-compared-google-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edefault%20search%20engine%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKira's%20aim%20is%20to%20introduce%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3Bfriction%26quot%3B%20into%20students'%20conversations%20with%20AI%20at%20the%20right%20stages%20so%20that%20they%20actually%20have%20a%20productive%20struggle%20and%20learn%20through%20the%20experience%2C%20Pasinetti%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20practice%2C%20that%20means%20Kira's%20platform%20can%20incrementally%20guide%20a%20student%20through%20a%20tough%20problem%20by%20calibrating%20itself%20to%20students'%20understanding%20of%20the%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKira's%20agents%20use%20these%20insights%20to%20inform%20teachers%20about%20student%20capabilities%20by%20building%20knowledge%20maps%20to%20determine%20what%20students%20know%20and%20don't%20know%20across%20a%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2298ff35ec-0197-4015-9607-67d9ad6d6c61%5C%22%3ESchools%20are%20getting%20tech-savvy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKira's%20business%20model%20banks%20on%20classrooms'%20growing%20embrace%20of%20not%20only%20AI%20and%20data%2C%20but%20tech-enabled%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20schools%20have%20begun%20implementing%20%26quot%3Badaptive%20learning%20technology%26quot%3B%20which%20can%20collect%20and%20leverage%20data%20on%20students'%20performance%2C%20progress%2C%20and%20learning%20style%20to%20tailor%20the%20learning%20experience.%20This%20technology%20aims%20to%20increase%20equity%20across%20the%20classroom%20and%20help%20teachers%20and%20students%20use%20time%20more%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20coincides%20with%20the%20widespread%20adoption%20of%20learning%20management%20systems%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20These%20are%20software%20programs%20that%20help%20educators%20design%20and%20manage%20online%20learning%20like%20Blackboard%2C%20Moodle%2C%20or%20TalentLMS.%20They%20surged%20in%20popularity%20in%202020%20and%202021%2C%20according%20to%20EducationWeek.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20EdWeek's%20survey%20of%201%2C000%20school%20district%20leaders%2C%20principals%2C%20and%20teachers%20conducted%20in%202022%2C%20only%206%25%20of%20educators%20said%20their%20school%20district%20didn't%20use%20an%20LMS.%20Schools%20can%20either%20integrate%20Kira%20into%20their%20existing%20LMS%20or%20use%20the%20platform%20as%20a%20standalone%20LMS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPasinetti%20said%20that%20by%20adopting%20Kira%2C%20schools%20can%20cut%20down%20on%20at%20least%20four%20to%20five%20pieces%20of%20software%20%E2%80%94%20often%20the%20most%20expensive%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKira's%20leaders%20see%20AI%20overhauling%20relationship%20between%20students%2C%20teachers%2C%20and%20technology%20%E2%80%94%20which%20could%20lead%20to%20more%20meaningful%20changes%20down%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20big%20shift%20that's%20happening%2C%20and%20especially%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20subject%20matter%20expertise%2C%20you're%20kind%20of%20learning%20alongside%20your%20student%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jagriti%20Agrawal%2C%20Kira's%20cofounder%20and%20vice%20president%20of%20artificial%20intelligence.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20that%20mindset%20could%20be%20a%20helpful%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandrew-ng-startup-wants-to-use-ai-agents-redefine-teaching-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745448654000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68095c6bc6ad288d147efb4a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandrew-ng-startup-wants-to-use-ai-agents-redefine-teaching-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kira%20Learning%20unveiled%20a%20new%20set%20of%20AI%20agents%20that%20will%20help%20teachers%20personalize%20their%20approach.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lvaranasi%40businessinsider.com%20(Lakshmi%20Varanasi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A65%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandrew-ng-startup-wants-to-use-ai-agents-redefine-teaching-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sam%20Altman's%20resignation%20from%20the%20Oklo%20board%20could%20pay%20off%20with%20a%20major%20OpenAI%20deal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Altman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68095daac6ad288d147efb79%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESam%20Altman%20stepped%20down%20as%20chairman%20of%20the%20OpenAI%20board%20on%20April%2022.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Hill%2FFilmMagic%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20stepped%20down%20as%20Oklo%20chairman%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAltman's%20exit%20allows%20OpenAI%20to%20pursue%20a%20power%20deal%20with%20Oklo's%20nuclear%20technology.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%2C%20valued%20at%20%24300%20billion%2C%20is%20expanding%20its%20data%20center%20business%20with%20new%20ventures.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-chatgpt-openai-ceo-career-net-worth-ycombinator-prepper-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman's%3C%2Fa%3E%20decision%20to%20step%20down%20as%20chairman%20of%20nuclear%20energy%20startup%20Oklo%20could%20set%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-data-center-infrastructure-hiring-push-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20CEO%20up%20to%20maximize%20his%20potential%20to%20profit%20from%20both%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-mind-of-sam-altman-openai-ceo-worldview-interviews-writing-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAltman%3C%2Fa%3E%20resigned%20from%20the%20Oklo%20board%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20company%20said%20in%20an%20SEC%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2Fix%3Fdoc%3D%2FArchives%2Fedgar%2Fdata%2F0001849056%2F000110465925037472%2Ftm2512904d1_8k.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiling%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20move%2C%20which%20the%20company%20said%20was%20not%20due%20to%20any%20disagreement%20or%20violation%20of%20its%20policy%2C%20paves%20the%20way%20for%20Oklo%20to%20one%20day%20enter%20into%20an%20agreement%20with%20OpenAI%20to%20power%20its%20AI%20technology.%20Oklo%20CEO%20Jacob%20DeWitte%20will%20take%20over%20for%20Altman%20as%20chairman%20of%20the%20board%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Altman%20off%20the%20Oklo%20board%2C%20OpenAI%20now%20has%20more%20range%20to%20pursue%20a%20power%20deal%20with%20the%20company.%20An%20early%20investor%20in%20Oklo%2C%20Altman%20still%20owns%20a%204.8%25%20stake.%20While%20he%20doesn't%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-reportedly-doesnt-own-equity-in-openai-chatgpt-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eequity%20in%20OpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20now%2C%20that%20could%20change%20in%20the%20future%2C%20especially%20as%20the%20company%20looks%20to%20transition%20from%20a%20nonprofit%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-why-openai-changed-nonprofit-model-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efor-profit%20corporate%20structure%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Altman%20gains%20equity%20in%20OpenAI%20and%20maintains%20his%20shares%20in%20Oklo%2C%20and%20the%20companies%20one%20day%20do%20a%20deal%20together%2C%20it%20could%20be%20a%20financial%20boon%20for%20the%20tech%20mogul.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20seems%20to%20be%20where%20this%20is%20moving%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bruce%20Kogut%2C%20the%20Sanford%20C.%20Bernstein%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20professor%20of%20leadership%20and%20ethics%20at%20Columbia%20Business%20School.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20OpenAI%20makes%20a%20deal%20to%20power%20a%20data%20center%20with%20one%20of%20Oklo's%20nuclear%20reactors%2C%20Kogut%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bpayments%20will%20be%20made%20to%20Oklo%20and%20returned%20to%20shareholders%2C%20which%20will%20include%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20Altman's%20departure%2C%20it%20may%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20Oklo%20and%20OpenAI%20to%20partner%20without%20added%20complexities%20posed%20by%20his%20role%20on%20the%20Board%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Oklo%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-data-center-infrastructure-hiring-push-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20is%20ramping%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0its%20data%20center%20business%20as%20it%20relies%20less%20on%20Microsoft%2C%20a%20major%20investor%20that%2C%20until%20recently%2C%20had%20ser