oltaics%2C%20because%20it%20is%20something%20they%20cannot%20see%20yet%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vimal%20weighs%20in.%20%E2%80%9CUnderstandably%2C%20individual%20farmers%20will%20always%20be%20anxious%20about%20installing%20these%20projects%20on%20their%20farms%2C%20but%20when%20a%20group%20of%20farmers%20comes%20together%20as%20an%20organisation%20and%20installs%20a%20solar%20farm%2C%20they%20will%20be%20able%20to%20reduce%20their%20electricity%20expenses.%E2%80%9D%20Only%20once%20farmers%20see%20the%20benefits%20in%20real%20time%20will%20it%20elicit%20a%20tacit%20acceptance%20of%20the%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVimal%20illustrates%20how%20farmers%20can%20capitalise%20on%20this%3A%20%E2%80%9CLet%E2%80%99s%20say%20farmers%20are%20currently%20buying%20electricity%20at%20Rs%208%20or%209%20per%20unit.%20Once%20they%20install%20agrivoltaics%2C%20electricity%20will%20be%20sold%20to%20them%20for%20Rs%205%2C%20which%20is%20cheaper.%20This%20way%2C%20they%20are%20minimising%20their%20expenditure%20and%20reducing%20their%20dependency%20on%20the%20grid.%E2%80%9D%20For%20farmers%20who%20are%20still%20apprehensive%20about%20the%20model%20going%20against%20the%20grain%2C%20Vimal%20has%20another%20solution.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fvideo.php%3Fheight%3D314%26href%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Faskagrivijay%252Fvideos%252F404259222478618%252F%26show_text%3Dfalse%26width%3D560%26t%3D0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22314%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgriVijay%20has%20launched%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20%E2%80%98Vertical%20Bifacial%20Solar%20AgriVoltaics%20Project%E2%80%99%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Next2Sun%20and%20Wattkraft%2C%20in%20Maharashtra.%20%E2%80%9COur%20innovative%20Agri-PV%20system%20is%20designed%20to%20simultaneously%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F420549%2Fbhaskar-solar-la