%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20now%2C%20while%20the%20main%20road%20just%20two%20kilometres%20away%20has%20an%20electricity%20line%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20chosen%20to%20remain%20off-grid.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20they%20came%20to%20ask%20if%20we%20wanted%20the%20line%20brought%20up%2C%20John%20kind%20of%20decided%20against%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20choice%20is%20rooted%20in%20both%20caution%20and%20conviction.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CIn%20those%20areas%2C%20the%20lines%20do%20keep%20falling%2C%20and%20they%E2%80%99re%20overhead%20lines.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20the%20fear%20of%20a%20live%20wire%20falling%20in%20the%20rain%20and%20someone%20stepping%20on%20it%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20quite%20a%20big%20issue%20in%20rural%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20since%20we%E2%80%99d%20already%20set%20up%20and%20realised%20how%20simple%20you%20can%20have%20it%20and%20still%20survive%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20just%20keep%20going%20with%20solar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20stream%20nearby%20was%20tapped%20for%20water%20and%20naturally%20filtered%20using%20gravel%20and%20charcoal.%20Rainwater%20harvesting%20became%20second%20nature.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20the%20power%20of%20water%20gravity%20to%20supply%20the%20entire%20homestay%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDEfaU4IzBRd%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDEfaU4IzBRd%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3C